{"tid":2375829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比芯片更可悲的行業，被日美全壟斷，終國公司連山寨版都造不出","createTime":"2021-01-22T10:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:31:14.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76ea50744aa2ac713e343b1f95ee1ae7f83a552f","tid":2375829,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"芯片產業是終國的一大短板，好在，如今在國家扶持、資本湧入的情況下，國產芯片走上了快速發展之路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0122%2Feb0568abj00qnb9md001ac000go00b4g.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0122%252Feb0568abj00qnb9md001ac000go00b4g.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=7b6bb778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  但是，我國還有一大短板，那就是科研儀器。而且，比起芯片，科研儀器行業更可悲。<br />\n<br />\n  為何悲哀？<br />\n<br />\n  據了解，終國90%的高端儀器被海外壟斷。在2018年全球科學儀器行業前20名中，終國企業無一上榜，全被美國、歐洲與日本企業所佔據。<br />\n<br />\n  其中，前十名的儀器製造商佔據了行業78%的銷售額，壟斷境況明顯。<br />\n<br />\n  研發週期長、規模小、技術壁壘極高，是科研儀器研發的三大特點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0122%2F7b08e13fj00qnb9md003yc000go00fdg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0122%252F7b08e13fj00qnb9md003yc000go00fdg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f186f85a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  作為全球第一的儀器製造商&mdash;&mdash;美國賽默飛，年銷售額僅為63.3億美元（折合人民幣410億元）。與高昂的研發費用、漫長的研發週期相比，這一回報並不能令人滿意。<br />\n<br />\n  因此，儀器設備成為了一個甚少有人關注的行業，資金投入、科研人員等，都十分緊缺。<br />\n<br />\n  終國冷凍電鏡之困<br />\n<br />\n  在科研儀器市場中，冷凍電鏡行業的落後尤為明顯，甚至連山寨版都做不出來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  冷凍電鏡是由傳統透射電子顯微鏡演變而來，冷凍電鏡加入了低溫傳輸系統與冷凍防污染系統。諾貝爾獎評選委員會評價道：低溫冷凍電子顯微鏡將生物化學帶入了一個新時代。<br />\n<br />\n  由此可見冷凍電鏡的重要性。在生物學、醫學、新藥研發等行業，冷凍電鏡有著十分關鍵的作用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0122%2Ff3c6b08cj00qnb9me001lc000go00cwg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0122%252Ff3c6b08cj00qnb9me001lc000go00cwg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=f2d9f6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  冷凍電鏡行業也已經形成壟斷態勢，荷蘭FEI（被賽默飛收購）、日本電子、日立這三家，在業界的壟斷地位明顯。尤其是FEI，幾乎是一家獨大。反觀國內，還沒有一家企業生產透射式電鏡，更不要提冷凍電鏡。<br />\n<br />\n  基礎薄弱<br />\n<br />\n  在稍低端的掃描電鏡領域，終國的市場佔比也不到10%，更不要提高端的冷凍電鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0122%2F27a939adj00qnb9mf0025c000go00cig.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0122%252F27a939adj00qnb9mf0025c000go00cig.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=55e43bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fe375762ca49c7a78fd8a25b344c931f8e9ee15","tid":2375829,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"支那人係短視+利益行先<br />\n淨係識得掉錢高薪挖個人返嚟 買現成器材<br />\n而唔係將呢啲錢擺落長遠發展 研發<br />\n抵阿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7619ce150666b2c151242ffa957b4b5ec46d0cf4","tid":2375829,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:28:33.000Z","msg":"支那人就係爛泥扶唔上壁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bdbd320106457392a2f8d5e9adbaf05dbbb890","tid":2375829,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:31:14.000Z","msg":"發展冷氣電競就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}